Hello!
Brief Description

Thank you very much for taking the time to look at my map. de_close is a defusal/aim map for CS:S. The map is close quarters and has fast combat situations.

In this map

The map contains one bomb site which separates the CT'S and the T's. There is also some cover at the left and right hand side of the bomb site for each team. The map was made in under 1 hour which is very obvious with its cube like design, however the point of this map was to see how much thrill the player can feel with its close quarters combat.

Originaly the idea came from a friend of mine who said and I quote "make an island where the cts bring on shore and the ts are in a forest".

Well after having ideas of my one this came up, a map where the terrorist beggin in a house made of logs, and the counter-terrorist are on boats.

I made this more real than the other maps, adding mountains (somewhat like spikes) a skybox, and environmental light.

It as a buyzone, but nothing else, making it a map for battle only.

Edit: Also, I don't think this is one of my good maps, since i made it in a short time and with few test, that is why i decided to make a version 2, with a bomb/defuse game more improved, as such, i will make more considrable space, since i wasted much on this map. I will add a second island, better sand, add more nature props, add a more irregular forest and house, and more plausable objects and barriers. The intend is to make a real life mission, so you can have fun in fantasise, so for this version, consider only that.

This is a map i made in my time off this winter, its got plenty of ways to go if you want to surprise the other team, it advertises 2girls1cup, cats and crazy santa-like chimney jumping, there are buyzones and a hidden gun just in case you run out of cash, bots seem to play the map pretty well if that's what you're into. It bears mild resembelance to cs_italy, very much in the T-spawn in the house, and also some in the building surrounding the map. It is very small and action starts right from the second you start the round. It's good for large amounts of players or just you and your friends on LAN servers, I made it and I know i'm being a bit biased, but trust me when i say its the most intense, fast played and camper unfriendly map since fy_poolday. it's the cat's pyjamas baby, merry christmas or happy hannuka

--------------------------
BLOODSTRIKE SOURCE
--------------------------

Bloodstrike is a classic map heralding back from the days of Counter-Strike 1.3 when it was recognized as the premier map for players who loved to die hard and come back into the fray quickly.

Bloodstrike Source a near perfect conversion of this classic map upgraded to a level of detail reserved for the Source engine. All of the textures are new and the map itself remains for the most part true to the original in terms of placement and scaling apart from some minor cosmetic additions.
